					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10323215#post-4163134</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10323215/scp-4907#post-4163134</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 23 Feb 2019 21:48:39 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Shaggydredlocks</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1722371</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The directness of the final note sapped it of any credulence, making it into an overbearing and unearned emotional beat that did not resonate in the slightest. I might have appreciated the sentiment had it not strayed from the established behavior of the anomaly, at the very least then it wouldn't have came off as quite a strong case of authorial intrusion.</p> <p>It made me unable to remain immersed, sending what may have been a sentimental moment into the throes of narmy talking down to the reader.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
